swfupload-rails-authentication
==============================

Demo Rails 2.3.2 app showing SWFUpload working in tandem with restful-authentication, CSRF protection and paperclip.

The demo has been updated to use SWFUpload v2.2.0 Beta 5, which supports Flash Player 10.

Requirements
============

Rails 2.3
ImageMagick
mime-types gem
paperclip gem


Usage
=====

rake db:schema:load
rake db:fixtures:load
script/server


Login
=====

